Kvisoft Products Pack 2015

Kvisoft provides easy but professional solutions to create Flash flip book, make Flash photo gallery, restore lost datas and convert videos between all kinds of formats. Your digital life will become easier and better with Kvisoft!




FlipBook Maker Version: 4.3.3



FlipBook Maker is a FlipBook software for converting PDF to magazine, creating digital publications, magazines and photo albums with page turning effect. Enhance your readers' experience with remarkable page flip magazines.



FlipBook Maker Pro Version: 4.3.3



Kvisoft Flipbook Maker Pro is a powerful HTML5 page flip software to convert your PDF into multimedia digital publications. It allows you to embed videos, images, audio, hyperlinks, hotspots and more multimedia objects to the output flipping pages



Data Recovery Version: 1.5.0



Safe data recovery software for Windows users to recover deleted or lost files, such as documents, videos, audio, archives and more from various kinds of file storage devices.



SWF to Video Converter Version: 1.5.0



Kvisoft SWF to Video Converter is a simple yet powerful flash to video converter that allows to convert any SWF to a wide range of video files easily, then you could view the output video files on any mobile device anytime and anywhere.



Flash Slideshow Designer Version: 1.5.0



Flash slideshow software to help you make a flash slide show or photo gallery from photos and videos with music in seconds.



Video Converter Version: 2.1.0



Kvisoft Video Converter supports audio and video conversion between almost all popular formats. It allows you tranform videos for various portable players. Except powerful video editing features, it also supports DVD ripping.



Video To Flash Converter Version: 2.1.0



Kvisoft Video to Flash provides you an quick way to convert your video files to Flash in FLV or SWF format. With it, video editing, video triming, video merging and more become more easier.



Flash Video Gallery Version: 1.5.6



Kvisoft Flash Video Gallery provides you an easy way to make interactive Flash photo galleries, video galleries or 3D Flash slideshow for business photo presentations, family photo albums, website Flash design.



Flash Photo Gallery Version: 1.5.6



Make amazing 3D Flash photo gallery with music and photos for onine sharing. You don't have to learn the complex Flash scripts, only with a few mouse clicks you can make an interactive 3D photo album or Flash photo gallery.




Supported OS: Windows 8/7/Vista/2000/XP
